{"vv24:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv24:0.2":"Itthivimana ","vv24:0.3":"Cittalatavagga ","vv24:0.4":"7. Uposathavimanavatthu ","vv24:1.1":"“Abhikkantena vannena, ","vv24:1.2":"ya tvam titthasi devate; ","vv24:1.3":"Obhasenti disa sabba, ","vv24:1.4":"osadhi viya taraka. ","vv24:2.1":"Kena tetadiso vanno, ","vv24:2.2":"…pe… ","vv24:2.3":"Vanno ca te sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv24:3.1":"Sa devata attamana, ","vv24:3.2":"…pe… ","vv24:3.3":"yassa kammassidam phalam. ","vv24:4.1":"“Uposathati mam annamsu, ","vv24:4.2":"saketayam upasika; ","vv24:4.3":"Saddha silena sampanna, ","vv24:4.4":"samvibhagarata sada. ","vv24:5.1":"Acchadananca bhattanca, ","vv24:5.2":"senasanam padipiyam; ","vv24:5.3":"Adasim ujubhutesu, ","vv24:5.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","vv24:6.1":"Catuddasim pancadasim, ","vv24:6.2":"ya ca pakkhassa atthami; ","vv24:6.3":"Patihariyapakkhanca, ","vv24:6.4":"atthangasusamagatam. ","vv24:7.1":"Uposatham upavasissam, ","vv24:7.2":"sada silesu samvuta; ","vv24:7.3":"Sannama samvibhaga ca, ","vv24:7.4":"vimanam avasamaham. ","vv24:8.1":"Panatipata virata, ","vv24:8.2":"musavada ca sannata; ","vv24:8.3":"Theyya ca aticara ca, ","vv24:8.4":"majjapana ca araka. ","vv24:9.1":"Pancasikkhapade rata, ","vv24:9.2":"ariyasaccana kovida; ","vv24:9.3":"Upasika cakkhumato, ","vv24:9.4":"gotamassa yasassino. ","vv24:10.1":"Tena metadiso vanno, ","vv24:10.2":"…pe… ","vv24:10.3":"Vanno ca me sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv24:11.1":"“Abhikkhanam nandanam sutva, ","vv24:11.2":"Chando me udapajjatha; ","vv24:11.3":"Tattha cittam panidhaya, ","vv24:11.4":"Upapannamhi nandanam. ","vv24:12.1":"Nakasim satthu vacanam, ","vv24:12.2":"buddhassadiccabandhuno; ","vv24:12.3":"Hine cittam panidhaya, ","vv24:12.4":"samhi pacchanutapini”ti. ","vv24:13.1":"“Kiva ciram vimanamhi, ","vv24:13.2":"idha vacchasuposathe; ","vv24:13.3":"Devate pucchitacikkha, ","vv24:13.4":"yadi janasi ayuno”ti. ","vv24:14.1":"“Satthi vassasahassani, ","vv24:14.2":"tisso ca vassakotiyo; ","vv24:14.3":"Idha thatva mahamuni, ","vv24:14.4":"ito cuta gamissami; ","vv24:14.5":"Manussanam sahabyatan”ti. ","vv24:15.1":"“Ma tvam uposathe bhayi, ","vv24:15.2":"sambuddhenasi byakata; ","vv24:15.3":"Sotapanna visesayi, ","vv24:15.4":"pahina tava duggati”ti. ","vv24:16.1":"Uposathavimanam sattamam. "}